{"tid":1458682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反思]文宣同花一樣","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:44:42.000Z","uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"832fb7afea3c6294a2612b2af1e1844662626ead","tid":1458682,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:42:07.000Z","msg":"文宣同花一樣，而人對花就係<br />\n<br />\n花多眼亂<br />\n貪新忘舊<br />\n轉眼即逝<br />\n<br />\n香港人不斷引起關注，終於睇到我地嘅努力令香港有所改變，但甘心我地冇盡用我地所做嘅行動所帶黎嘅回響？<br />\n<br />\n有好多大事小事，以及荒謬嘅事，我地都太容易令佢流走，根本冇足夠時間發酵，尋根究底，搵出背後目的。<br />\n<br />\n今日發生大事，聽日又有，後日都有，不斷重復。幾乎冇時間好好比我地，比市民，比任何人消化事件。<br />\n<br />\n香港人係善忘，記住成件事嘅過程係好難，但係我地可以將過程總結成結果，令市民只要聽到事件就聯想起結果。每一次行動之後比一段時間，比人諗下，要經過思考先會記憶猶新。<br />\n<br />\n個人建議<br />\n行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;  文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;  討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣先係一個完整運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ddba937bc82202e362341784a3b2de7a0ba9e0","tid":1458682,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"回帶係一個唔錯方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4090b4c0148539c63e190395cdefbe68b5689010","tid":1458682,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5332fba1152b43543504498d4d2fe59e5f443e1b","tid":1458682,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85156881bbe41c4d2d0b0df3bc56f61f8c4bc256","tid":1458682,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi